Symbol.Script_3D:
! Air Cooled Rotary Chiller
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
operatedMode = 0 addStatus = 0 IF GLOB_CONTEXT > 40 AND GLOB_CONTEXT < 50 THEN operatedMode = 1 addStatus = 3 ENDIF
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -boxLength/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -boxLength/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2, B/2, legHeight+boxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -boxLength/2, B/2, legHeight+boxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -boxLength/2, -B/2, legHeight+boxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2, -B/2, legHeight+boxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, -sideBoxDepth/2, legHeight+0.10, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, sideBoxDepth/2, legHeight+0.10, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, -sideBoxDepth/2, legHeight+0.10+sideBoxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, sideBoxDepth/2, legHeight+0.10+sideBoxHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- SUPPORT --- !
ADD -boxLength/2, -B/2, 0 ROTy -90 CUTPOLYA 5, 2, 0, legThick, legThick, 15, legThick, B-legThick, 15, legHeight-legThick, B-legThick, 15, legHeight-legThick, legThick, 15, legThick, legThick, -1 DEL 1
num = INT(boxLength/2.5) IF NOT(ABS((num/2)-INT(NUM/2)) < EPS) THEN num = num-1 IF num < 2 THEN num = 2 cutLength = (boxLength-(num+1)*legThick)/num
FOR i = 1 TO num ADDx (legThick+cutLength)*(i-1) ROTx 90 CUTPOLYA 5, 2, 0, legThick, legThick, 15, legThick+cutLength, legThick, 15, legThick+cutLength, legHeight-legThick, 15, legThick, legHeight-legThick, 15, legThick, legThick, -1 DEL 2 NEXT i
PUT 0, 0, 15 PUT boxLength, 0, 15 PUT boxLength, B, 15 PUT 0, B, 15 PUT 0, 0, -1 FOR j = 1 TO num PUT legThick+(legThick+cutLength)*(j-1), legThick, 15 PUT legThick+cutLength+(legThick+cutLength)*(j-1), legThick, 15 PUT legThick+cutLength+(legThick+cutLength)*(j-1), B-legThick, 15 PUT legThick+(legThick+cutLength)*(j-1), B-legThick, 15 PUT legThick+(legThick+cutLength)*(j-1), legThick, -1 NEXT j
PRISM_ NSP/3, legHeight, GET (NSP)
FOR i = 1 TO num+1 CUTEND NEXT i
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ADDz legHeight BLOCK boxLength, B, boxHeight DEL 2
ADD -lowerBoxLength/2, -lowerBoxSize/2, legHeight/2-lowerBoxSize/2 BLOCK lowerBoxLength, lowerBoxSize, legHeight/2+lowerBoxSize/2 DEL 1
ADD boxLength/2, -sideBoxDepth/2, legHeight+0.10 BLOCK sideBoxThick, sideBoxDepth, sideBoxHeight DEL 1
! --- GRILL --- !
num = INT((boxLength-0.15*(boxLength/5.20))/(cylindDia*1.1)) IF num < 2 THEN num = 2 cylindDist2 = (boxLength-0.30*(boxLength/5.20)-cylindDia)/(num-1)
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN FOR k = 1 TO num ADD -boxLength/2+0.15*(boxLength/5.20)+cylindDia/2+cylindDist2*(k-1), -cylindDia/2-cylindDist, legHeight+boxHeight EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, cylindHeight, addStatus+16+32, 0, 0, 901, cylindDia/2, 360, 4001 ADDz cylindHeight IF operatedMode < EPS THEN GOSUB 500 DEL 1
ADDy cylindDia+cylindDist*2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, cylindHeight, addStatus+16+32, 0, 0, 901, cylindDia/2, 360, 4001 ADDz cylindHeight IF operatedMode < EPS GOSUB 500 DEL 3 NEXT k ELSE FOR k = 1 TO num ADD -boxLength/2+0.15+cylindDia/2+(cylindDia*1.1)*(k-1), -cylindDia/2-cylindDist, legHeight+boxHeight EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, cylindHeight, 1+2+16+32, 0, 0, 901, cylindDia/2, 360, 4001
ADDy cylindDia+cylindDist*2 EXTRUDE 2, 0, 0, cylindHeight, 1+2+16+32, 0, 0, 901, cylindDia/2, 360, 4001 DEL 2 NEXT k ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 12, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 12 END
500: SegmetAng = 360/SegmentsNum SegmetHalfAng = SegmetAng/2 TotalInsideRad = Rad-HalfThick/TAN(SegmetHalfAng)-Thick DivisionInsideDist = (TotalInsideRad-Thick*(DivisionNum-1))/DivisionNum
ROTz SegmetHalfAng
PUT 0, 0, 901 PUT Rad, 360, 4001
alpha = 0 FOR i = 1 TO SegmentsNum InsideDist = DivisionInsideDist CenterPointPosX = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha) CenterPointPosY = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha) FOR j = 1 TO DivisionNum InsideDist = InsideDist+Thick*(j>1) PointOnArcEndPosX = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)-(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha) PointOnArcEnd2PosX = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)+(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha) PointOnArcEndPosY = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha)+(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha) PointOnArcEnd2PosY = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha)-(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)
IF j = 1 THEN PUT CenterPointPosX, CenterPointPosY, 1 PUT PointOnArcEndPosX, PointOnArcEndPosY, 1 PUT 0, 0, 901 PUT PointOnArcEnd2PosX, PointOnArcEnd2PosY, 3001 PUT CenterPointPosX, CenterPointPosY, -1 ELSE InsideDist = InsideDist+DivisionInsideDist OPointOnArcEndPosX = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)-(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha) OPointOnArcEnd2PosX = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)+(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha) OPointOnArcEndPosY = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha)+(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha) OPointOnArcEnd2PosY = (HalfThick/SIN(SegmetHalfAng)+InsideDist*COS(SegmetHalfAng))*SIN(alpha)-(InsideDist*SIN(SegmetHalfAng))*COS(alpha)
PUT PointOnArcEndPosX, PointOnArcEndPosY, 1 PUT 0, 0, 901 PUT PointOnArcEnd2PosX, PointOnArcEnd2PosY, 3001 PUT OPointOnArcEnd2PosX, OPointOnArcEnd2PosY, 1 PUT 0, 0, 901 PUT OPointOnArcEndPosX, OPointOnArcEndPosY, 3001 PUT PointOnArcEndPosX, PointOnArcEndPosY, -1 ENDIF NEXT j alpha = alpha+SegmetAng NEXT i
POLY_ NSP/3,
GET(NSP)
DEL 1 RETURN
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Air Cooled Rotary Chiller
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 boxLength/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -boxLength/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -boxLength/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 boxLength/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, sideBoxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 boxLength/2+sideBoxThick, -sideBoxDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConShow_1=0, ConEdit_1 = 12, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConShow_2=0, ConEdit_2 = 12 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Air Cooled Rotary Chiller
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
IF A < 3.40 THEN A = 3.40 IF B < 0.70 THEN B = 0.70 IF B > A THEN B = A
legThick = 0.10
lowerBoxSize = 0.50 lowerBoxLength = 3.20
cylindHeight = 0.15 cylindDia = 1.00*(B/2.30) cylindDist = (B-cylindDia*2)/4 Rad = cylindDia/2 Thick = 0.02 HalfThick = Thick/2 SegmentsNum = 6 DivisionNum = 4
sideBoxDepth = B-0.20 sideBoxThick = 0.20 sideBoxHeight = boxHeight-0.20 boxLength = A-sideBoxThick
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z

! Air Cooled Rotary Chiller
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_attr[4][4] FOR i = 1 TO 4 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 2 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14

! Air Cooled Rotary Chiller
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0

PARAMETERS ZZYZX = legHeight+boxHeight+cylindHeight LOCK "ZZYZX"
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !

ConID = 1 ConName = `Труба Впускного Соединения `

ConWVecX = 1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0

VALUES "ConPosX_1" RANGE [-lowerBoxLength/2+ConWidth_1/2, -ConWidth_1/2-legThick/2] PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = -lowerBoxSize/2 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = legHeight/2 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
! --- 2nd CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 2 ConName = `Труба Выпускного Соединения`
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = -1 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ConWidth_2 > lowerBoxSize THEN ConWidth_2 = lowerBoxSize VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE (0, lowerBoxSize] PARAMETERS ConDepth_2 = ConWidth_2 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_2" VALUES "ConLength_2" RANGE [B/2-lowerBoxSize/2, ]
VALUES "ConPosX_2" RANGE [ConWidth_2/2+legThick/2, lowerBoxLength/2-ConWidth_2/2] PARAMETERS ConPosY_2 = -lowerBoxSize/2 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_2 = legHeight/2 ENDIF

ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_2, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
